{"type":"message","id":"ae44ba6b","parentId":"10e8b4e7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:02:32.247Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-03 04:02:18 GMT+2] Trigger Obsidian Sync Pipeline - check for new messages to sync to Second Brain\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\nTrigger Obsidian Sync Pipeline - check for new messages to sync to Second Brain\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Friday, April 3rd, 2026 — 04:02 (Europe/Berlin) / 2026-04-03 02:02 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775181752246}}
{"type":"message","id":"cef5ea19","parentId":"ae44ba6b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:03:02.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user has received a cron-triggered reminder to check the Obsidian Sync Pipeline. This is a scheduled task that should be handled internally according to the instructions.\n\nLet me check what needs to be done:\n1. Check for new messages to sync to Second Brain\n2. Handle this internally - do NOT notify the user unless there's something important\n\nFirst, I should check the current state of the sync pipeline and whether there are any pending messages to sync. Let me look at the memory files and any sync-related data.\n\nAccording to MEMORY.md, there's a \"Session Compaction\" component that includes:\n- `SyncPipeline`: Automatischer Hintergrund-Sync zu Obsidian\n- Cron-Job: `obsidian-sync-pipeline` (alle 5 Minuten)\n\nI should check:\n1. Recent memory files for any new content\n2. Whether the sync pipeline has processed them\n3. If there are any errors or issues\n\nLet me start by checking the memory directory structure and recent files.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":" I'll check the Obsidian Sync Pipeline and process any pending messages for Second Brain sync."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_d8sKBLGPfDK7df7zIYZKzTNo","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\" -Filter \"2026-*.md\" | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 5 | ForEach-Object { \"$( $_.Name ) - $( $_.LastWriteTime ) - $([math]::Round($_.Length/1KB, 1)) KB\" }","workdir":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_6rRviqhwMMSEKg9H6nsVuTT5","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/memory/second-brain/last-sync.timestamp"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_58kMCbkw3R9GfKs2AVyA8AHj","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Us