{"type":"message","id":"15fbb4ca","parentId":"421b8318","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:03:53.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"   The Second Brain vault exists. Now I need to:\n\n1. Initialize the sync infrastructure (create the memory/second-brain directory)\n2. Check today's memory content for anything important to sync\n3. Update the last-sync timestamp\n\nLooking at the 2026-04-03.md memory file, it contains:\n- Critical Bug Discovery about the `edit` tool parameter issue\n- This is important technical documentation\n\nI should sync this to the Second Brain Inbox. Let me set up the sync tracking and copy relevant content.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_xm9u1xCSb6YOvbaxELDeOm8m","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\second-brain\" -Force","workdir":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_EY8RiWUo5XXtCTpu57La9YA6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/memory/second-brain/last-sync.timestamp","content":"{\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-03T02:02:00Z\",\n  \"entries_synced\": 1,\n  \"sync_source\": \"cron-pipeline\",\n  \"last_sync_from\": \"memory/2026-04-03.md\"\n}\n"}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":18854,"output":255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19109,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775181820960}}
